reviewText: A true and very moving story.  The young girl playing the role of Annie is captivating.  Annie's story of discovery and ultimate freedom shouldn't be missed.  I knew the story going into the viewing, and was pleased to see it was done beautifully.
Will not play on the two main DVD players.  I borrowed a portable DVD player and this movie will play on this.  Shouldn't the DVD play on all of my DVD players?
